&lt;li&gt;Experience operating CNC equipment (lathe or mill)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated critical thinker&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience handling parts from programming through completed machined part&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
