&lt;li&gt;Experience in an aerospace machining environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with modern multi-axis CAM packages is a plus.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of modern high speed machining strategies and tooling.&lt;/li&gt;
