&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-teams=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;Ursa Major was founded to revolutionize how America and its allies access and apply high-performance propulsion, from hypersonics to solid rocket motors, satellite maneuvering and launch. We design and deliver propulsion and defense systems that solve the most urgent and critical national security demands.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a motivated Expeditor to join our team. The ideal candidate will have an enthusiastic approach to Inventory Control. You must be willing to match our fast-paced cadence and thrive with rapid change.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As an Expeditor you are aiming to efficiently bring hardware into and out of the ERP system and always keep inventory accuracy at 100% while executing daily requests. You will be responsible for ensuring the accurate transactions of all hardware in and out of Ursa Major facilities. You will support basic ERP transactions, escalate any identified nonconformance and ensure hardware is delivered safely on time, and with clear traceability within the facility. ERP accuracy and improvement is our continual goal which will drive many projects you are tasked with.&lt;/p&gt;
