&lt;li&gt;Perform daily cycle counts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assistance with periodic full physical inventory counts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify low stock levels, do preliminary investigation into shortage and escalate when necessary.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Execute engineering approved edits to Manufacturing Orders within ERP&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Shipping and receiving; including scanning and filing,&amp;nbsp;updating ERP receipts,&amp;nbsp;stocking shipping materials,&amp;nbsp;packaging outgoing hardware, and scheduling shipments and&amp;nbsp;pickups.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate with internal stakeholders and routing deliveries to their intended recipients.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assisting teams on projects and improvements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain a clean, organized, and efficient workspace.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Experience / Requirements:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exceptional organization and communication skills, both written and verbal.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Able to lift and transport parts and tools weighing up to 50lbs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Valid driver’s license.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;High School diploma or GED&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency with computer software and ability to learn new programs.&lt;/li&gt;
