&lt;li&gt;Code must be well organized, commented, and maintainable&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop code blocks that are to be designed for reuse with standardized devices&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Program and configure facility automation and SCADA applications, connecting to standard networking and databasing configurations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create electrical schematics and oversee the build of new industrial electrical control panels which are NFPA79/NEC/UL508A compliant. Select electrical and electromechanical components such as servo motors and controllers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
